UI/UX Requirements

Styling Consistency
    Maintain design token alignment with previous steps:
        rounded-2xl, shadow-md, hover:shadow-lg, transition-all duration-300
    Feed max-width: max-w-2xl centered with mx-auto for a focused reading column
    Card backgrounds: bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 with a subtle border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700

Dark Mode
    Use Tailwind's dark: utilities throughout all components
    Sync with the theme persistence established in Step 4 (AppearanceSettings)
    Ensure avatar fallback colors, action button icons, and media overlays remain accessible in dark mode

Responsive Behavior
    Mobile (< 640px): full-width cards, touch-friendly tap targets (min 44px), stacked layout
    Tablet (640px–1024px): centered column at max-w-xl
    Desktop (> 1024px): centered column at max-w-2xl; CreatePost card is sticky at top

Animations & Transitions
    Like button: scale bounce (scale-125 → scale-100, duration-150) on toggle
    CommentSection expand/collapse: max-height transition (transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-in-out)
    New post prepend: slide-down + fade-in animation (translateY(-8px) → translateY(0), opacity-0 → opacity-100, duration-200)
    Skeleton loaders: animate-pulse with bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 blocks

